        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Microelectronics Research for Energy Innovation Act of 2022 or the Micro Act of 2022</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Energy to carry out a program, which includes workforce training and development, to accelerate research for designing, developing, and manufacturing next-generation microelectronics.</p>]]></text>
